    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but resting doesn't change the fact that the cycle always starts again. i'm just waiting for the next crash. it feels like i'm just running in place until i eventually collapse. there's no actual progress, just a temporary pause before the next failure. it feels like the loop is inevitable.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
